{"tid":2272750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]應該點稱呼班反熱狗又有熱狗餘毒嘅人","createTime":"2020-11-05T08:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T06:14:13.000Z","uid":57911,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed2a79158939f3dfe674e4b1de56c3014113c5e","tid":2272750,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:53:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的，熱狗禍害之深令唔少人或多或少仲抱有熱狗價值觀<br />\n但當中好多人已經變做反熱狗同憎熱狗<br />\n宜家大多數情況香港人都會直接稱呼佢哋做熱狗<br />\n佢哋會好嬲甚至屌返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n因為依個稱呼將佢哋同陳雲黃洋達拉埋同一個層次<br />\n就算話佢哋熱狗餘毒未清<br />\n只要個名有熱狗兩個字都令佢哋十分反感<br />\n<br />\n所以想徵求各位連登仔意見<br />\n想睇下應該點稱呼之餘又唔會令佢哋太過反感<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e94488ec0d8e36643d2fba92fb0d6614eac0d3b","tid":2272750,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:54:48.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918fdad2d4c8c308b148d3b4e16026a46f6e8edf","tid":2272750,"uid":23758,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"咪即係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣咁倒米"},{"pid":"1fec1e84e8dfef91a6512eae9c12343243406bc8","tid":2272750,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"918fdad2d4c8c308b148d3b4e16026a46f6e8edf","tid":2272750,"uid":23758,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:54:55.000Z","msg":"咪即係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣咁倒米"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:59:36.000Z","msg":"會嬲唔可以直接叫熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a078f9cf76ee6bf46c4b5c7caaa7a10f1720f61e","tid":2272750,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"033d213dd287c9725443e2cd5ef76a5d64ed3738","tid":2272750,"uid":156724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:09:3